## ðŸ§  Key Patterns

### Edit Operations (RELIABLE)
```
# DON'T use native edit tool (exact match fails)
edit path "exact text that must match" â†’ FAILURE

# DO use file-edit.py with fuzzy matching
fe text path.md "partial text" "new text" --fuzzy â†’ SUCCESS
```

### Search Operations
```
# Primary: memory_search for prior work
memory_search "edit failures" â†’ Returns memory files with context

# Secondary: qmd for semantic search
qmd search "topic" -c memory â†’ Indexed, with context

# Tertiary: rg for fast keyword search
rg "pattern" â†’ Raw speed, no context
```

### File Operations
```
# New content: write tool
write path.md "full content"

# Partial read: fe with range
fe read path.md --start 10 --end 20

# Edit specific line: fe line
fe line path.md 15 "new content"

# Verify changes: fe verify
fe verify original.md modified.md
```

